<subSubSection id="2EC7E06AA81FEA172DE3D15793A5D21E" pageId="0" pageNumber="63" type="distribution">
<paragraph id="2A37E06F1604B07006D19E354D141E11" pageId="0" pageNumber="63">Distribution and habitat.</paragraph>
<paragraph id="F2418A6BFA931B889BDE17E62B509874" pageId="0" pageNumber="63">The species was observed to grow on dry and partially shaded limestone, around the karst forest edge, at 700-900 m elevation.</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
